replies.body:
Your early game relies on ganks (unfortunately). However, once you hit 6, you ought to be able to easily kill him. Once he blinds you, sweep him (if he flashes, then hookshot after him). After that, ult him. By then, his blind will have worn off and be on cooldown, so you will easily be able to out-damage him :)

I hope this helps :)

